The Word always told us that they said, "Hey, this is what's coming."But my job is to continue to tell you.

00:27:30.679 --> 00:27:40.798
It wasn't the 23rd, it wasn't the 24th, and we're still here, but He said, "Occupy until He comes. It's all hands on deck.

00:27:40.799 --> 00:27:46.319
He wants a harvest."And people argue and say, "Brandon, it's a great falling away."I didn't say there wasn't.

00:27:46.320 --> 00:27:52.956
The Bible says there would be, but He's still going after—leaving the 99 to go after the one.

00:27:52.957 --> 00:28:07.278
And I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, we're about to see the former and latter rain like we've never seen before, with one final push. And I believe that started on the 23rd.

00:28:07.279 --> 00:28:15.512
I believe we saw it this week on Sunday when He said, "As of this week and Charlie's funeral and all the things."And here we are, we're seeing it.

00:28:15.513 --> 00:28:24.479
And here we are, tomorrow's Friday, and we see all the things, and He said, "Watch the fig tree.

00:28:24.480 --> 00:28:33.084
Watch the fig tree."It all started over there. It started over there, and it's going to end over there.

00:28:33.085 --> 00:28:36.809
It's about the people of Israel. It's about the Jewish people.

00:28:36.810 --> 00:28:41.936
Do you see it, ladies and gentlemen? It started there, and it will end there.

00:28:41.937 --> 00:28:47.999
And here we see all these people say, "We want a two-state solution. We want to divide Jerusalem.

00:28:48.000 --> 00:28:56.155
We want to do all these things and have a Palestinian state."And it's all about Jerusalem, just like it was thousands of years ago.

00:28:56.156 --> 00:29:04.879
They're still fighting and still doing all the stuff they've ever done, but it's all about the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ now.

00:29:04.880 --> 00:29:11.914
So what will Benjamin say tomorrow? I don't know, but I think it's interesting, don't you?

00:29:11.915 --> 00:29:18.845
It's the week. Nobody could five months ago, six months ago; they won't even—do you understand?

00:29:18.846 --> 00:29:28.158
That is strategic. Look at that. The Lord, it's like Sister Billie always says, 'Oh, what a plan. Oh, what a planner.'That's 'Oh, what a plan.

00:29:28.159 --> 00:29:47.260
Oh, what a planner.'And you start getting things before they are even announced in the news, and you start praying over things six or seven months in advance, and you go, 'Only God, only God'concerning the week of the 23rd, and here we are, and it's almost over.

00:29:47.261 --> 00:29:54.005
What did we see? We see a lot of dividing, and we see a lot of things, rumors of wars.

00:29:54.006 --> 00:30:04.668
Russia saying, 'We're ready to kick this thing off at another level.'The United States saying, 'We're about to do what we're going to do to you,'and everybody's flexing right now.

00:30:04.669 --> 00:30:12.588
You've got the big gorillas in the room. They say, 'You're going to do this,'and 'We're going to do this.'And I'm going, 'Oh, we don't want any of this.

00:30:12.589 --> 00:30:22.200
We want peace.'But at the same time, you see the war drums being beaten, just like the Lord told us. Do you remember that vision?

00:30:22.201 --> 00:30:31.918
I saw Turkey, and they started beating these massive drums, boom boom, and the war drums started sounding all throughout the land.

00:30:31.919 --> 00:30:48.702
And then I saw biological weapons coming up out of Israel, out of Damascus to attack with a mustard gas spraying the Jewish people, and they sprayed them, and it was the most horrific thing I've ever seen.

00:30:48.703 --> 00:30:59.918
But as that happened, coming out of Damascus, Damascus becomes a ruinous heap. They glow in the dark—I'm talking bad.

00:30:59.919 --> 00:31:09.998
And then Turkey will come to Syria's defense, and they'll become like a wounded brother. He'll be a wounded brother.

00:31:09.999 --> 00:31:19.759
And I saw Turkey and these other Arab nations saying, 'You shouldn't have done that.'And it is actually a foot-troop war.

00:31:19.760 --> 00:31:29.131
I saw soldiers marching against Israel. But the hand of the Lord defended Israel in the days ahead.

00:31:29.132 --> 00:31:34.158
I saw they were planning something in the middle of the night.

00:31:34.159 --> 00:31:44.158
And you remember all this if you prayed with us for a time. I saw that was coming out of the sides of mountains in Iran.

00:31:44.159 --> 00:31:50.465
And they had trucks full of this stuff, semi-trucks. And they were bringing those trucks, and they were bringing it in secretly.

00:31:50.466 --> 00:31:59.686
And they're in 50-gallon drums, planning an attack worse than October 7th—another wave.

00:31:59.687 --> 00:32:08.644
And the Lord said, 'You must pray. You must pray.'Do you remember this?

00:32:08.645 --> 00:32:32.182
Even before the escalation with Iran and Israel in the days past, when that 12-day war, whatever it was, and then Trump said peace, but I saw another plan coming—another planned attack, another major event will come worse than October 7th, worse, the Lord warned us.

00:32:32.183 --> 00:32:45.207
And remember, we pray over this. Our job is always a call to prayer, not a call to fear. People don't understand the purpose of our channel.

00:32:45.208 --> 00:32:51.951
Our channel is to pray and to intercede, but God shows us what to pray about and what's coming.

00:32:51.952 --> 00:33:07.437
And I just believe, as we pray for America, that as we stand with Israel in the days ahead, there's a retaliation within—a Red Dawn experience.

00:33:07.438 --> 00:33:13.623
Remember that. I've told you this. I've said these words so many times that it is over the top.

00:33:13.624 --> 00:33:22.286
A Red Dawn experience, a Pearl Harbor type of event. Remember, and I warned you all. I said, 'Remember Pearl Harbor?

00:33:22.287 --> 00:33:32.165
It was when people did not expect it.'A Red Dawn event, the enemy within, the enemy within ten major cities.

00:33:32.166 --> 00:33:44.434
To pray over these major cities, to pray over our nation for Homeland Security, FBI, our local sheriff's department, to uncover the demonic.

00:33:44.435 --> 00:33:49.885
And look what happened in New York a couple of days ago with the secret communication.

00:33:49.886 --> 00:34:03.754
And I said, 'Remember when I told you all I saw secret communication?'They were communicating in a way that was not able to be detected, and they find 100,000 SIM cards, and they find all this stuff.

00:34:03.755 --> 00:34:11.953
That's a way that they were obviously communicating. But is there more? Probably. I said it's well-funded.

00:34:11.954 --> 00:34:24.874
They used on the news the exact words that we've been praying over: 'well-funded.'This looks like not just this group of people, but it was through crypto and all these other things.

00:34:24.875 --> 00:34:33.918
And then the Lord showed us all that we've been praying over this stuff for—what is it, almost over a year now?

00:34:33.919 --> 00:34:41.519
We've been interceding, and what we were praying over is in the news.

00:34:41.520 --> 00:34:50.555
When you have government officials on a TV thing quoting the same thing we got in prayer, you know you're on the right road.

00:34:50.556 --> 00:34:57.118
Praying over college campuses, praying over major sporting events—I've told you about the drones.

00:34:57.119 --> 00:35:05.617
I saw them flying into stadiums and being set off. How many times have I said 'major public gatherings'to pray over this stuff?

00:35:05.618 --> 00:35:14.935
And the Lord has warned us over and over and over again. So that's just what I have to say about all that, y'all.

00:35:14.936 --> 00:35:20.194
But I just think it's interesting as we pray and we seek His face.

00:35:20.195 --> 00:35:28.499
He said, 'If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways.'And that's what I believe we're doing.

00:35:28.500 --> 00:35:31.676
And then He's warned us about earthquakes. He's warned us about major earthquakes.

00:35:31.677 --> 00:35:38.083
We had another huge earthquake. He's talking about earthquakes and shakings in Seattle and in British Columbia.

00:35:38.084 --> 00:35:48.190
He's talking about major financial things coming, a major plague coming. He warns us and warns us and warns us as a good father should.

00:35:48.191 --> 00:35:58.879
If we, being evil, give good gifts to our children, how much more does our Heavenly Father love us and give good gifts to us?

00:35:58.880 --> 00:36:07.199
If we will be that good and we want to bless our kids, how much more does He? But He warns you. How long He gave Noah and them?

00:36:07.200 --> 00:36:16.078
A hundred-plus years, a hundred years of warning before something major happened.

00:36:16.079 --> 00:36:22.035
Most people, within just six months, they go, 'Well, I don't remember that word. I remember it's false. You know, I don't know about that.

00:36:22.036 --> 00:36:32.984
I didn't hear it.'Kim Clement gave that word about Esther or whatever that was about Erica 14 years prior before it manifested.

00:36:32.985 --> 00:36:37.866
And I'm sure people back then thought, 'Kim is off. He is false.

00:36:37.867 --> 00:36:43.158
He ain't hearing God.'Listen, Kim Clement now, he's not even here.

00:36:43.159 --> 00:36:51.617
He went home to be with the Lord. But his word that he gave clear back in 2011 is manifesting today.

00:36:51.618 --> 00:36:58.939
And it's one of the most accurate prophetic words that I can hear of this generation, but he's not even here.

00:36:58.940 --> 00:37:07.131
His daughter is, and his family. But do you understand? It's not always in your timing.

00:37:07.132 --> 00:37:12.639
It's not a microwave; it's a slow cooker. But God is faithful.

00:37:12.640 --> 00:37:21.055
And when you're calling these things out and you're saying what's coming, and they say, 'Well, I didn't see it in six months'—because I get persecuted a lot.

00:37:21.056 --> 00:37:33.003
They say a lot, but yeah, there's a lot going on. And so, all that to say this: you're always going to have haters.

00:37:33.004 --> 00:37:36.997
Haters are going to be hating. That's it. But my job is to keep praying.

00:37:36.998 --> 00:37:47.025
And I'm thankful for every single one of you that have come to pray with us and intercede for the nations, because I believe the power of prayer changes things.

00:37:47.026 --> 00:37:57.567
I believe the power of prayer changes things, don't you? For sure. Yep. No question.

00:37:57.568 --> 00:38:02.719
And we're about to see something we've always dreamed of with the glorious church.

00:38:02.720 --> 00:38:15.151
I have such an anticipation to see my Asian people, my friends, get born again and have a radical move of God in the Asian community.

00:38:15.152 --> 00:38:21.458
As we keep preaching, folks, we had another 20 get saved, we had five.

00:38:21.459 --> 00:38:45.754
It seems like sometimes when you only get 20 people born again in South Korea and five born in China, I go, 'Oh, Lord, are we making any?'But the Lord said, 'Brandon, five here, five here, five here, 20, 20, 20 adds up to a lot over time, because then they're going to tell their families, and it's generational change.'It's generational change.

00:38:45.755 --> 00:39:05.519
And I think, but God, we need tens of millions. Help me, Lord, to have a greater influence, a wider tent, a wider capacity to reach the Asians for you, to reach the Africans, to reach the South Americans, to reach the people for you.

00:39:05.520 --> 00:39:12.176
You know, I get excited about this. Braden and I, we were all dancing.

00:39:12.177 --> 00:39:18.479
I told Diana, 'We got 20! We got 20! We got 20!'We were dancing around, we're so excited.

00:39:18.480 --> 00:39:26.313
20 people got born again tonight, you know, because we do the live over there in the middle of the afternoon.

00:39:26.314 --> 00:39:32.615
Braden stays up and does everything and translates it and talks to them.

00:39:32.616 --> 00:39:41.009
They hear, 'You speak such good South Korean.'No, we don't, but we're trying.

00:39:41.010 --> 00:39:54.479
We're really trying so hard. We don't speak Russian. We don't speak German. We don't speak Japanese, but we try to get them for Jesus.

00:39:54.480 --> 00:40:00.793
If we can get one—I say every time we do it, if we just get one, wouldn't that be wonderful?

00:40:00.794 --> 00:40:05.822
If we can just get one that was so lost that they just found Jesus tonight.

00:40:05.823 --> 00:40:13.710
If we could just get one for him, but we get 20, and I'm so excited. And then we'll get 500 here or a thousand.

00:40:13.711 --> 00:40:21.439
But our whole job is to tell you Jesus loves you and that he has a plan for your life.

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:28.159
When I tell you these visitations, they're really private for me. They're really private for Diana.

00:40:28.160 --> 00:40:45.804
But we become vulnerable so that people can maybe just get a little something, taste and see that the Lord is good, because he's been good to Brandon and Diana. When I tell you these angel stories, it's not just me.

00:40:45.805 --> 00:41:12.159
There are other people I know, but I tell you this stuff and I'm very open about it, you know, about the truck going down the road this last time, telling you about how Diana was pregnant with our daughter and God showed up and showed off for us when we didn't have no gas in our truck and the angel of the Lord pushed us to the gas station.

00:41:12.160 --> 00:41:19.131
Those are precious moments, moments that changed Diana and I and the children forever.

00:41:19.132 --> 00:41:24.408
Braden—Megan's still overcoming—but Braden, it changed him forever.

00:41:24.409 --> 00:41:32.559
And it's still so precious when you get a dog raised from the dead.

00:41:32.560 --> 00:41:49.118
And my thing, when I told you all that no matter how much you fast, no matter how much you pray, no matter how much you think yourself righteous after you do that, your righteousness is as filthy rags.

00:41:49.119 --> 00:41:58.078
You are only holy and only able to do what you're able to do by grace.

00:41:58.079 --> 00:42:00.792
It's something you don't earn and something you don't deserve.

00:42:00.793 --> 00:42:04.153
It's grace, ladies and gentlemen. That's what I was trying to tell you.

00:42:04.155 --> 00:42:19.439
No matter how much you think you can fast to become ready—and, boy, I tell you what, I fasted, I prayed, I took communion four times today, and I'm qualified to raise the dead.

00:42:19.440 --> 00:42:23.993
It's not about you. It's not about how much you are righteous.

00:42:23.994 --> 00:42:30.916
It's about him. He became sin for you. He became sick for you.

00:42:30.917 --> 00:42:43.441
He became poor for you; through his poverty, through his holiness, he made a way for you. No, it wasn't about you and how much you did.

00:42:43.442 --> 00:42:54.559
Because that's what I try to tell you: no matter how holy you think you are, your holiness is nothing compared to what he did.

00:42:54.560 --> 00:43:03.999
He was without sin. He became sickness, he became sin for you.

00:43:04.000 --> 00:43:10.069
So, that's what I was trying to get across to you, no matter how much I flipped out that night acting crazy.

00:43:10.070 --> 00:43:27.780
Diana, I tell you, she was there freaking out, thinking, 'I just killed the dog.'And then my little girl's going, 'Daddy, just pray.'And I'm thinking God is not going to hear me.

00:43:27.781 --> 00:43:48.399
I just flipped out and I'm a total fool right now. God, I'm sure he's up there shaking his head going, 'Oh, Brandon.'But even in my lowest moment, I was trying to tell you, even in my lowest moment, his grace was enough.

00:43:48.400 --> 00:44:08.479
His mercy is enough. Even in your lowest moment—you may be the worst drug addict, alcoholic, gambleraholic, whatever it may be—his grace is enough for you to wash you clean.

00:44:08.480 --> 00:44:18.078
It's something you don't earn and it's something you don't deserve. His grace is enough for you.

00:44:18.079 --> 00:44:27.983
You may have the worst sexual problem, and you may be looking at the worst stuff on the internet possible, but his grace is enough for you.

00:44:27.984 --> 00:44:36.631
If you just confess your sins, he is faithful and just to forgive you of your sins and cleanse you of all unrighteousness.

00:44:36.632 --> 00:44:57.712
And that's what I was trying to get across that night: even in my weirdo sin, when I was freaking out and yelling at my kids and acting like a fool, and they're all looking at me going, 'Dad just lost it,'cussing and acting up because I just killed my dog, God showed up and showed off and raised that dog from the dead.

00:44:57.713 --> 00:45:13.548
Even in my moment of embarrassment, his grace is enough for you. And he does. And what's amazing is it wasn't about a dog.

00:45:13.549 --> 00:45:23.439
Even whenever you say it's him washing your sins, washing your life, making you whole again—do you understand what that takes to get that done?

00:45:23.440 --> 00:45:27.199
No, you don't. It was by grace. You received by grace through faith.

00:45:27.200 --> 00:45:34.343
You didn't earn it. You didn't deserve it. But it cost Jesus his life. And that's what I was trying to tell you all.

00:45:34.344 --> 00:45:49.199
No matter how much I thought what qualified me—what qualified me, ladies and gentlemen, for raising the dead, casting out devils, doing whatever I got to do to think that I'm qualified today?

00:45:49.200 --> 00:45:56.190
Boy, I tell you what, I haven't cussed in the last 48 hours. I haven't done—in fact, Diana and I, we've been acting great together.

00:45:56.191 --> 00:45:59.984
Do you not see that we're doing really good? Our marriage is awesome.

00:45:59.985 --> 00:46:12.029
I haven't been cranking her, she hadn't been cranking me, and we're qualified now to go around laying hands on all the people at the churches, and we're going to get everybody healed by the power of God through us because we've done it.

00:46:12.030 --> 00:46:20.379
And I'm telling everybody we're qualified. But the moment I looked at her cross and she looked at me crying like, 'Well, why are you being great with me?'well, we just disqualified ourselves.

00:46:20.380 --> 00:46:25.919
'God can't use us.'Now, that's what the enemy tries to tell you.

00:46:25.920 --> 00:46:32.479
'Well, you know, self-doubt. You had a little bit of an anger issue there.

00:46:32.480 --> 00:46:46.490
You're not qualified anymore.'That's what I was trying to tell y'all, because he'll always come to try to disqualify you in your own thoughts, to make you second-guess, thinking, 'Well, God's not going to use me, Diana.

00:46:46.491 --> 00:46:57.329
I'm sorry. He's not going to use me tonight on YouTube. I can't go on there because, you know, I got mad at the guy at the restaurant or whatever.'Do you understand?

00:46:57.330 --> 00:47:05.279
The old man's always trying to get back up. The old man is always trying to get out of that grave, but you die daily.

00:47:05.280 --> 00:47:13.039
And no matter how much you mess up, his grace is enough for you.

00:47:13.040 --> 00:47:17.221
I'm not saying practice sin and think you can act like a fool all the time—I'm not saying that.

00:47:17.222 --> 00:47:22.959
But if you do mess up, you run to God when you sin; you don't run away from him.

00:47:22.960 --> 00:47:40.318
And there is nobody here that doesn't have some gossip thing going on where you're running and slandering Sister Clipboard, and you're going, 'Well, you know, Sister Clipboard is at church at the hall monitor station over there, and I walked in and she's like, "Well, you're late."'And, boy, she just ticked me off.

00:47:40.319 --> 00:47:59.356
Sister Clipboard was watching, and I came into church today, and she saw I was late, and she's over there being her holy self saying, 'I strode up 30 minutes before church got started, and here you are running in late with your kids trying to put them in children's church, and Sister Clipboard's over there taking note of how many times you come in late on church.

00:47:59.357 --> 00:48:07.015
See, you're not qualified to be the head prayer person at the church this week because you were late five times this last Sunday, or over the last month.

00:48:07.016 --> 00:48:15.103
And so I've been watching, taking note, and I turned it into the pastor, just telling you that you're not ready and you're not qualified.'It's the truth.

00:48:15.104 --> 00:48:18.587
And you're always going to have some Sister Clipboard up there doing that.

00:48:18.588 --> 00:48:25.296
It's hall monitor Christians. Do you know how many... And now I look at... You go into a store, they're always looking.

00:48:25.297 --> 00:48:30.057
'I've seen you somewhere, brother.'And I'm like, 'I've got to hide myself.'I'm just Brandon.

00:48:30.058 --> 00:48:37.679
I just want to go and just pray. Well, he showed up late. Sister Clipboard's always looking.

00:48:37.680 --> 00:48:44.658
I'm trying to help you all. Does that make sense, what I'm trying to say?

00:48:44.659 --> 00:48:51.199
You're never going to get there on your own. It's all about Jesus. It's all about His blood.

00:48:51.200 --> 00:48:57.919
And Sister Clipboard can put her clipboard up, and you can go in there and just be you and say, 'Jesus, here am I.

00:48:57.920 --> 00:49:10.399
Send me.'Either you believe it or you don't. But there's always going to be somebody trying to disqualify you, always.

00:49:10.400 --> 00:49:15.958
You know what I get? Because I even get people to say, 'You know, I'm done talking bad about you.'That's what I got from a brother.

00:49:15.959 --> 00:49:19.940
I say, 'Well, I didn't know you were talking bad about me in the first place.

00:49:19.941 --> 00:49:27.126
I'm not going to ridicule you no more. I'm not going to run you down.'I say, 'Well, praise God. Praise God, brother. I'm glad.

00:49:27.127 --> 00:49:32.879
I didn't know that you were talking trash about me in the first place.'Well, praise the Lord.

00:49:32.880 --> 00:49:44.234
But you get that and you go, 'Well, I didn't realize you were talking trash about me, but I'm so glad that you're not anymore.'But you get what I'm saying?

00:49:44.235 --> 00:49:51.298
'Well, I didn't feel like you're qualified enough.'I didn't qualify myself.

00:49:51.299 --> 00:49:59.077
Jesus did. I'm just Brandon. And He'll use whoever He wants to. Does that make sense, what I'm trying to tell y'all?

00:49:59.078 --> 00:50:03.313
There's always going to be somebody behind the scenes saying, 'You're not qualified.

00:50:03.314 --> 00:50:09.000
You're not good enough.''Well, he didn't go to Bible school.

00:50:09.001 --> 00:50:16.580
He didn't spend five hours praying in the Spirit this morning. And I sure didn't see him at the altar crying.

00:50:16.581 --> 00:50:29.999
Unless he shed a couple of tears, he ain't ready.'I just say, 'Okay.'So, I just try to be real with y'all because I deal with it, too.

00:50:30.000 --> 00:50:44.159
And that's called spiritual Pharisees. And they always try to say, 'Who are you? Who are you?''Well, I don't know. I'm Brandon. I showed up.

00:50:44.160 --> 00:50:58.433
I love you.'Well, you know, 'You came to the right place if you were looking for something a little humorous, I guess, but cracking me up.'Well, because you do, because you live in it with me, too, and you see what we see.

00:50:58.434 --> 00:51:08.297
And I'm telling you, I am so beyond the political correctness of churchianity and church Pharisaism.

00:51:08.298 --> 00:51:23.585
I've come to tell you that Jesus likes the people who don't have a spiritual ego and just have a... 'I may have a little dirt on me, but I'm here for you, Father.

00:51:23.586 --> 00:51:36.318
And I may have a little bit of a scrape on my knee, but I love you, Lord, and I just want to help you out.'Versus the one that comes in that has the hood on going, 'Oh, I'm here.

00:51:36.319 --> 00:51:46.418
I've been fasting. All right, let's pray.'Not trying to be funny.

00:51:46.419 --> 00:51:52.019
I'm trying to paint a picture because I'm telling you, you disqualify yourself.

00:51:52.020 --> 00:51:57.118
And I don't know who I'm talking to tonight, but I felt this is for somebody.

00:51:57.119 --> 00:52:02.843
Stop disqualifying yourself. You never were good enough in the first place.

00:52:02.844 --> 00:52:11.279
It was always by His grace. And His grace is enough for you, lady.

00:52:11.280 --> 00:52:20.498
His grace is enough for you, sir. And He loves you. And He will polish you up if you stay on that potter's wheel.

00:52:20.499 --> 00:52:31.919
And you'll go, just like I talk about, from glory to glory. He's changing us, changing us, changing us.

00:52:31.920 --> 00:52:40.558
His likeness and image to perfect in me, the love of God shown to the world.

00:52:40.559 --> 00:52:48.639
For He's changing, He's changing me from earthly things to the heavenly.

00:52:48.640 --> 00:52:55.501
His likeness and image to perfect in me, the love of God shown to the world.

